<h2>Refund Processed</h2>
<p>Hello <strong>{{userName}}</strong>,</p>
<p>Your refund of <strong>₹{{refundAmount}}</strong> has been initiated successfully. Refunds are typically credited within 5–7 business days depending on your bank.</p>

<div class="details-box">
  <div class="details-row">
    <span class="label">Original Order ID</span>
    <span class="value">{{orderUniqueId}}</span>
  </div>
  <div class="details-row">
    <span class="label">Refund Amount</span>
    <span class="value">₹{{refundAmount}}</span>
  </div>
  <div class="details-row">
    <span class="label">Reason</span>
    <span class="value">{{refundReason}}</span>
  </div>
  <div class="details-row">
    <span class="label">Status</span>
    <span class="value">Processing</span>
  </div>
</div>

<p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact our support team.</p>
<a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="btn">View Dashboard</a>
